==English==

===Etymology===
From {{der|en|NL.|Onchocerca|pos=a genus of parasitic worms}}, from {{der|en|grc|ὄγκος||barb}} + {{m|grc|κέρκος||tail}} + {{affix|en|-iasis}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ɒŋkəsɜːˈkaɪəsɪs/|lang=en}}

===Noun===
